data.description: You will never want to leave this beautiful house located in Clayton with close to 2000 sq ft with a hard to find in-ground kidney shape pool! It's as if this home was just built. The new kitchen offers new appliances, granite counter tops and beautiful cabinets. The bathrooms is completely new with cabinetry, fixtures, flooring and a beautiful tile shower. Other updates include: New windows, New gutters, New water heater, New plumbing and electrical throughout house, New interior doors, New flooring, New lighting, New fixtures, lots of storage and so much more. House is located on an acre lot with no rear neighbors. Finished basement with close to 650 sq ft. Don't delay, set your appointment or feel free to call if you have any questions.
